title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2008-12 Merecedes C-Class [W204] LED Tail Lights
description: This video demonstrates how to install a set of Spyder Auto's Light Bar type LED Tail lights for the W204 Mercedes Benz C-Class. This fits 2008-10 C-Class as well as 2011-12 C-Class models. The installation method is the same for either year range, but the wiring harness connection differs. This complete walkthrough tutorial guides you through the install process from start to finish.
tags: Spyder LED Tail Lights, how to install, Mercedes C-Class, LED lights, spyder
